modules.name: Halogen.HTML.CSS
modules.comments:
This module defines an adapter between the `purescript-halogen` and
`purescript-css` libraries.

declarations.comments:
Render a set of rules as an inline style.

For example:

```purescript
H.div [ CSS.style do color red
                     display block ]
      [ ... ]
```
declarations.title: style

declarations.comments: Render a set of rules as a `style` element.
